      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-D4BA5F6B-A3D8-4A41-997B-31E1316C5320" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Cash settlement – Actual movement of funds between bank accounts enabled via F110 run, APM, Payment batching and SAP MBC to send the payment files to the IC Vendor
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C45ACCED-C0A5-4B1E-8A9B-07413406DD38" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Financial Posting will be replicated realtime from individual S4 box to CFIN system
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-41DF064A-28CC-4BFA-8F5E-7AFA2BDEE81C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>For Control Countries (e.g., India, China, Vietnam) Mandatory for CASH Settlement
For Non-Control Countries: Company Codes which do not have inhouse bank relationship
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8E9EBB19-C660-4EC6-B68B-59E498CE8CB5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Tax Posting in S/4</text>
      </textAnnotation>
